query:
/*+ NoMergeJoin(q1 s t1 tq1 u1 b) NoHashJoin(acc b q1 s t1 tq1 u1 a1) */ select acc.location,
count(*)
from question AS q1
inner join tag_question AS tq1
on q1.id = tq1.question_id AND q1.favorite_count >= 1 AND q1.favorite_count <= 10
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = q1.site_id AND s.site_id = tq1.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('blender',
'ell',
'gaming',
'graphicdesign',
'travel')
inner join tag AS t1
on s.site_id = t1.site_id AND t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND t1.name IN ('adobe-photoshop',
'cycles',
'minecraft',
'modeling',
'python',
'visas')
inner join so_user AS u1
on s.site_id = u1.site_id AND u1.downvotes >= 10 AND u1.downvotes <= 100000
inner join badge AS b
on s.site_id = b.site_id AND b.user_id = u1.id AND b.name IN ('Autobiographer',
'Civic Duty',
'Cleanup',
'Curious',
'Enthusiast',
'Excavator',
'Explainer',
'Good Question',
'Mortarboard',
'Organizer',
'Quorum',
'Scholar',
'Self-Learner',
'Vox Populi')
inner join account AS acc
on acc.id = u1.account_id
inner join answer AS a1
on s.site_id = a1.site_id AND a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND q1.id = a1.question_id group by acc.location order by count(*) desc LIMIT 100;
